Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.39,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:20.20,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.48,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:04.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.19,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:22.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:27.27,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:34.21,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Misonoo Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks so plain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so clumsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She trips so elegently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She is no good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves her right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't become discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama is truly great. Such majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who were the ones bad mouthing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Misonoo-san, what did Miya-sama say just then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,6. Lost and Alone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, what time was it on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You'll be baking a cake with Tomoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That... well, we may postpone it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were looking forward to it so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an English quiz next week... and we are both busy with our clubs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you enjoying school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our usually talkative Nanako doesn't say much about her school lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I'm enjoying it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so different from Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I'm enjoying it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so different from Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been slandered by people I don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot write a letter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could possibly meet you some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to assemble at the gymnasium because of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hoped the class was canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead there is strength-testing today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My bag is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It has my gym clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I left it here this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, daughter of a rat dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, pornographer's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand back her gym bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have hidden it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop with the nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I want to do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you must have left it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, you're getting absent-minded due to being chosen as a Sorority member.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't accuse her. There is no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ok, I can borrow gym clothes from a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend? Tomoko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can go on ahead. To the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But will she lend you her gym clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be avoiding you lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you two... have a quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! She'll help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally we can talk! I've been worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When I called you last night. I was told you were already asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you called out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if I could borrow your gym clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My gym clothes aren't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't be appropriate for a Sorority member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are no longer the Nanako I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps someone else could loan you some gym clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To expel Miss Misonoo from the Sorority due to her being chosen unfairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sign here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see her expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't she have signed it herself? That would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey... Arikura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you in junior high school with Misonoo-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How did she get chosen? You must know all her dirty tricks...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell me... please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She has none.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,None. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely none!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Nanako and her family very well! They don't use dirty tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I never!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to make such a fuss about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened to you, Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate me just because I was chosen as a Sorority member!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Tomoko refused. I knew she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san! Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't get them? Why? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't bring hers today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, then come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can borrow them from a big sister for you. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Class is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've lost my gym clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to borrow some from...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem, I'm leaving early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to the hospital to have some follow-up tests done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I may look healthy but I'm still recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These might be big for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.28,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They had a certain sweet and clean smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...with the crisp touch of Biyakudan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I found myself entirely encircled by Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All that morning, I felt I had the ability to keep on going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In the afternoon, the rain stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and my only remaining class was English.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I planned on going home early and washing Kaoru-no-Kimi's gym clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was feeling much better...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I started feeling a little bit happier too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to buy a notebook before class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, twenty yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a second, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you Miss Misonoo, a freshmen, section B?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We are sophomores.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to speak to you a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I should probably get back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My class is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! It would be wise to obey us while we're still reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you don't pay attention, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Resign from the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Resign, of your own volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand why, don't you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even attend the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have been chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't permit such an injustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Injustice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no injustice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not an injustice, how could it have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We, too, once were candidates for the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We faced the selection process fairly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...but were not chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...still we have our pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow your conscience. Think on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...Dear Brother, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked into those eyes and saw hearts filled with hatred and anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and despair, jealousy... even sorrow, such as I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear that someday I could become like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding! Surely you're not serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nanako, that's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't leave the Sorority! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ask Miya-sama to let me leave tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, members have been disowned,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...but no one in their right mind has left willingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You absolutely can't! Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is. My sports bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait till tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving the Sorority is utterly unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you quit, you would be giving in to the rumors and slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect you from those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always be happy to extend my hand on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't quit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you enjoying school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You plan to bake a cake with Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you called out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if I could borrow your gym clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My gym clothes aren't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't be appropriate for a Sorority member.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like school at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this ok? Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I want to stop at the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, later...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't endure this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The music box?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:20:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It just can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so unbelievable?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I was just thinking how I wished I could see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then! Perhaps it isn't true after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you doing, out so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Well... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually you'll tell me in a letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll send you home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rather late for a high school student to be out alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about tomorrow and the day after?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No one hurts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No one hates me, or slanders me, or scoffs at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hate anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I am neither angry, nor jealous, nor crying over being slandered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that. My life is peaceful and happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:23:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If somehow you saw me crying, it must have been over something minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have been quite fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, whatever happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And also Tomoko... so I can't be unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko, my friend since childhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:14.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:19.52,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.99,0:24:25.12,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.12,0:24:30.60,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.33,0:24:36.87,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:42.34,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.34,0:24:45.08,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.08,0:24:47.88,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.88,0:24:50.28,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.28,0:24:55.55,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.43,0:25:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako flees to the clock tower, trying to escape her tormentors...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.17,0:25:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...only to find it already occupied by Saint-Juste, and her mysterious smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.64,0:25:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Nanako sees that Saint-Juste is holding a handful of sharp knives...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.98,0:25:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The Darkness in the Clock Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.20,0:25:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
